longBusinessSummary: ChargePanel AB (publ) provides a SaaS platform for the operation and management of electric vehicle charging networks. It offers ChargePanel Enterprise, ChargePanel Cloud, and ChargePanel Connect for Charge Point operators and e-mobility service providers. The company also provides ChargePanel Go, a managed EV charging services; EV fleet management software and services; and EV roaming. It offers its platform for businesses, charge point operators, e-mobility service providers, energy companies, installers, organizations, and resellers. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
